Task 5: Personal Loan Acceptance (Customer Segmentation)Objective: Predict which customers are most likely to accept a personal loan offer from a marketing campaign.Key Skills: Semicolon-Delimited Data Parsing, Decision Tree Classification, Business Intelligence.Technical Challenges Overcome: * Identified and fixed a ValueError caused by a semicolon-separated (sep=';') dataset format that was preventing column recognition.Resolved a KeyError by verifying that the 'job' column was hidden within a single-string row due to incorrect delimiters.Outcome: A Decision Tree model that segments the customer base, allowing the bank to target specific job categories and age groups for maximum campaign ROI.
